Request review from @TheBlueMatt and @morcos

@TheBlueMatt - you introduced the vtxConflicted vector in BlockConnected in 461e49fee2935b1eb4d4ea7bae3023e655c0a6d8 with comment 'This change adds a parameter to BlockConnectedDisconnected which lists the transactions which were removed from mempool due to confliction as a result of this operation. While its somewhat of a shame to make block-validation-logic generate a list of mempool changes to be included in its generated callbacks, fixing this isnt too hard.'

@morcos - you attempted something similar in #9240

